<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>What psychic ability or insider information do you have that lets you know what SoE was intending to do by changing Charm in this manner?</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
You are assuming that they are doing this to stop Soloing, but clearly, that is not what it's going to do, as Charm/Aggro/Reg kiting still persist as well as root/dot. Making everything a summoning mob would pretty much put an end to this, except for charm and fear kiting. To stop those two, charm would have to be made unreliable again (highly) and all planar mobs would have to be made fear immune.<br>
<br>
So, I pose to you that your assumption that SoE is doing this to stop soloing is incorrect, or incomplete. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ninjacorp.com/Rhasin_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pissed1vi2soe@themagicianstower>Pissed1VI2SOE</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 556<br> <font color=#333333>(1/14/03 7:52:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=447.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   hmm</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> There's a second thread because the first was to notify us that there was a change incoming... which was then hijacked by the &quot;I told ya so's&quot; and &quot;It's the whiney magician's fault!&quot; If you have something to contribute to this thread by all means... otherwise head back to the first one.  <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
